<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77d6a1b8-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s69j"><num value="69j">§ 69j.</num><heading> Application of other laws</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this subchapter shall be held to be in addition to, and not in substitution for or limitation of, the provisions of any other Act of Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77d6a1b9-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/act/1951-08-08/ch298/s12">Aug. 8, 1951, ch. 298, § 12</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/65/181">65 Stat. 181</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
